data.description: Gorgeously updated 3BR/BA 1.5 story wing & gable home on 2 lots features kitchen w/ quartz counters, island w/ hi-top seating, SS appliances & walk-in pantry! Home was completely refinished down to studs w/ improvements such as new structural beams, wiring & elec. box, insulation, plumbing, central A/C, vinyl windows, siding, roof, appliances, cabinetry, int/ext doors, front deck, landscaping & much more completed between 2021 & 2023. Modernized floor plan w/ kitchen open to LR. Primary bedroom & bath w/ walk-in tiled shower on 1st floor. Cozy fam-room walks out to spacious back yard w/ paver patio & 2-stall garage. 2nd floor offers 2 large bedrooms & bonus office/lounge space.
